</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-55_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-56_ pf-text-1"><strong>Hands-on training </strong>- Practical sessions that simulate real-life scenarios.




































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-58_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regular refresher courses</strong> - To ensure first aid skills and knowledge are current, refresher courses should be undertaken at least every three years.




































</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-60_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-61_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-62_ pf-heading-1-h3">Importance of tailored first aid training
