</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-79_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-80_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regular drills</strong> - Conducting regular emergency response drills to ensure everyone knows their role in an emergency.






































